OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,Fis due to become Wales' next First
OL,6,FMinister, taking the reins from after
OL,7,Fhis five-year tenure.
OL,9,FSo far, all of Wales' leaders have
OL,10,Fbeen men - and from the Labour Party.
OL,11,FITV1's spoke to those with experience
OL,12,Fof the role to find out what advice
OL,13,Fthey have for the next FM.
OL,15,F1) Take our advice
OL,17,F"Listen to people, engage with
OL,18,Feverybody," said Alun Michael, Wales'
OL,19,Finaugural First Secretary (now First
OL,20,FMinister).
