OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,FHe added: "Be clear about what you are
OL,6,Ffor - what are your priorities? What
OL,7,Fare you really there for? Share that
OL,8,Fas clearly as possible."
OL,10,F"Inspire," is the advice of Carwyn
OL,11,FJones. "Inspire confidence, inspire
OL,12,Fhope and confidence in your judgement."
OL,14,FThe widow of the late Rhodri Morgan,
OL,15,FJulie Morgan MS, says not to panic.
OL,16,F"Stay calm and do your best. It's a
OL,17,Fgreat opportunity."
OL,19,F2) Prepare for questions from
OL,20,Fexperienced backbenchers
