OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,FAlthough , he has not ruled out being
OL,6,Fa rebel.
OL,8,FHe told Sharp End: "I think the people
OL,9,Fdeserve a short period of silence, as
OL,10,Fthey say, I don't think I'll be
OL,11,Fdashing to do it straight away but
OL,12,Fthere are two years to go."
OL,14,FThe FM who lead Wales through the
OL,15,FCovid pandemic and lockdowns is
OL,16,Flooking forward to taking his seat on
OL,17,Fthe back-benches and to "have a bit of
OL,18,Ffreedom".
