OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,FMr Drakeford said: "I'm not planning
OL,6,Fto be a rebel particularly but I'm
OL,7,Flooking forward to a chance to say
OL,8,Fsome things that are not as easy to
OL,9,Fsay when you're confined by the
OL,10,Fresponsibilities that you have as
OL,11,FFirst Minister."
