OL,5,F2018 - 2024: Mark Drakeford
OL,7,F3) It can be lonely but don't isolate
OL,8,Fyourself
OL,10,F"You have to make sure you don't cut
OL,11,Fyourself off from people," Carwyn
OL,12,FJones warns. "It's very, very easy to
OL,13,Fcut yourself off from your own
OL,14,Fbackbenchers - not deliberately but
OL,15,Fbecause you never see them.
OL,17,F"You only see them once a week in a
OL,18,Fmeeting and you have to make time to
OL,19,Fsit in the tea room in the Senedd,
OL,20,Ftalk to people.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/15
