OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,F"There are lots of aspects of the job
OL,6,Fthat most people wouldn't want to do -
OL,7,Fthere is an element of loneliness
OL,8,Fthere - you are the person taking the
OL,9,Fdecision, but I had a supportive
OL,10,Ffamily around me, I was home most
OL,11,Fnights and living 20 miles away that
OL,12,Fwas really important for me, but it's
OL,13,Fpart of the job and you accept it."
OL,15,FMr Drakeford said: "In the end it is
OL,16,Fyou who carries the can.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/15
