OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,F"There are moments when, as you walk
OL,6,Ftowards a camera or you walk towards a
OL,7,Fpodium, you think, 'It's me then, I'm
OL,8,Fgoing to be doing this' and that can
OL,9,Fbe a bit lonely."
OL,11,F4) Look the part, but don't think
OL,12,Fyou're more important than others
OL,14,F"You have to be your own person,"
OL,15,Faccording to Mr Jones.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/15
