OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,F"Rhodri was a great influence on me,
OL,6,Fand I always regarded him as a father
OL,7,Ffigure to me in politics, but you have
OL,8,Fto carve out your own niche. For me it
OL,9,Fwas about inspiring confidence in
OL,10,Fpeople."
OL,12,FHe added: "You have to look the part -
OL,13,Fwe can talk about how people shouldn't
OL,14,Fvote for personalities over policies
OL,15,Fbut it doesn't work that way. If you
OL,16,Fdon't look the part, they won't vote
OL,17,Ffor you - that's important."JJulie
OL,18,FMorgan described how her late husband
OL,19,FRhodri was "very much against status".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/15
