OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,FShe said: "He felt that if you thought
OL,6,Fyou were important, that's the end for
OL,7,Fyou in politics.
OL,9,F"He felt it was really important that
OL,10,Fpoliticians don't think they're
OL,11,Fimportant - that they keep in touch
OL,12,Fwith the people.
OL,14,F"Wherever he used to go, people used
OL,15,Fto come up to him and talk to him and
OL,16,Fhe liked it! He didn't feel it was
OL,17,Fintrusive at all."
