OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,FAhead of one of his penultimate FMQs,
OL,6,FMr Drakeford reflected on how
OL,7,Fdifficult it is in Wales to give other
OL,8,Fpeople in the Cabinet profile beyond
OL,9,Fthe first minister.
OL,11,FHe said: "I remember conversations
OL,12,Fwith Rhodri where he used to say he
OL,13,Fwas very determined, particularly with
OL,14,Fthe women he had in his Cabinet, to
OL,15,Ffind a way for them to become better
OL,16,Fknown to people in Wales.
OL,18,F"But he cast a very long shadow and
OL,19,Fthe job casts a long shadow."
