OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,FIn an ITV Cymru Wales poll, 11% of
OL,6,Fpeople thought Vaughan Gething should
OL,7,Fbe the next leader of the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment, compared to 72% who did
OL,9,Fnot know who should be the next first
OL,10,Fminister.
OL,12,F"In some ways I'm not surprised," Mr
OL,13,FDrakeford said. "I wonder how many
OL,14,Fpeople on the Grangetown omnibus can
OL,15,Fname five members of the UK cabinet.
OL,17,F"Particularly in a modern media world,
OL,18,Fwith the person who is at the head of
OL,19,Fit all, it's difficult for other
OL,20,Fpeople to get the profile for
OL,21,Fthemselves."
