OL,5,F6) Know when it's your time to go
OL,7,F"It's best to go before you're pushed"
OL,8,F- that is what Rhodri Morgan used to
OL,9,Fsay.
OL,11,FHis widow, Julie, said: "(Rhodri)
OL,12,Fthought it was best to give somebody
OL,13,Felse a chance and I think he left in a
OL,14,Fvery positive way.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/15
