OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,F"I think he was looking forward when
OL,6,Fhe actually went to never wear a suit
OL,7,Fagain or a tie. He gave away his
OL,8,Fdinner suit, he said he never wanted
OL,9,Fto see an airport again (but he did go
OL,10,Fback on that!) he didn't like the
OL,11,Fformal bits of a public figure really
OL,12,Fand he was looking forward to a time
OL,13,Fwhen he could be out in the garden, he
OL,14,Fcould have chickens, he could do all
OL,15,Fthe sorts of things that he loved
OL,16,Fdoing."
