OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,FAlun Michael's time at the helm lasted
OL,6,Fonly nine months. He said: "When I
OL,7,Fresigned, I did find it quite a shock
OL,8,Fand it's actually quite nice to have a
OL,9,Fperiod when you can reflect and take a
OL,10,Flittle more time when thinking things
OL,11,Fthrough."
OL,13,FWhen Carwyn Jones became FM in 2009,
OL,14,Fhe told himself he wouldn't do the job
OL,15,Ffor more than 10 years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/15
