OL,3,CHow to be Wales' First Minister
OL,5,FHe said: "I went on holiday in the
OL,6,Fsummer of 2017 and I knew then that I
OL,7,Fwas beginning to think eight years is
OL,8,Fa long time in this job. Some people
OL,9,Fknew, but I announced I was going in
OL,10,FApril 2018 at the Welsh Labour
OL,11,Fconference and I did the round of
OL,12,Fmedia interviews.
OL,14,F"Afterwards I went to a pub with my
OL,15,Fteam, sat down, and it was as if a
OL,16,Fweight had been lifted off my
OL,17,Fshoulders. I knew then that it was the
OL,18,Fright decision."
